<div class="bg-f3">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="toggles toggles-style3 toggle-box">
            <div class="toggle-item">
                <div class="toggle-heading clearfix"><strong>Required documents for incorporating a company in
                    Malta</strong></div>
                <div class="toggle-content">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Certified true copy of passport</li>
                        <li>Utility bill showing exactly the residence address, which should not be older than 3
                            months.
                        </li>
                        <li>Bank reference- which should state that the person is of a good morale character and
                            trustworthy
                        </li>
                        <li>Professional reference (Bank refererence/ Reference letter) Criminal record a recent one.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
